		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>Please consider my Zapato Power series with Freddie Ramos. Freddie is Hispanic and he lives in a multicultural community of immigrants. These chapter books, published by Albert Whitman, are for newly independent readers and feature a sprinkling of Spanish and a boy with super-powered purple sneakers and dreams of being a superhero. Thank you for including Albert Whitman and other smaller, independent publishers on your updated list.</p>
